(http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/sbdb.cgi?sstr=elenin;orb=1;cove=1;log=0;cad=1#cad) 
   if you guys want to see where it will be and when, what we got to watch 
out for  from this "brown dwarf star" called Elemi, is of it sending solar 
flares around  the this month, causing quakes, moving the earth out of its 
orbit, and stealing  us from our own sun. Ect.  Sept. is another bad time, we 
got to stay inside  too.  You can check the chat, and move it through the 
different days by  moving the sliding bar to see where it will be on each day. 
 Don't  know about you guys, but I am praying Earth stays safe from it's 
pull.  sf
